        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You fire a green ray at your target. Make a spell attack. You deal 12d10 damage, and the target must attempt a basic Fortitude save. On a critical hit, treat the save result as one degree worse. A creature reduced to 0 HP is reduced to fine powder; its gear remains. An object you hit is destroyed (no save), regardless of Hardness, unless it's an artifact or similarly hard to destroy. A single casting can destroy no more than a 10-foot cube of matter. This automatically destroys any force construct, such as a wall of force.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d10.</p>"
